Package fr.insalyon.geometry

Class GeoCoordinates

java.lang.Object
fr.insalyon.geometry.GeoCoordinates
public class GeoCoordinates extends Object
Represents geographical coordinates with latitude and longitude values. Differs from Position as the coordinates are in a spherical coordinate system and not in a Cartesian system.
